        public cs131.pa4.Abstract.Tunnel admit​(cs131.pa4.Abstract.Vehicle vehicle)
        Description copied from class: cs131.pa4.Abstract.Scheduler
        Attempts to admit the given vehicle in one of the scheduler's tunnels. If there is no tunnel available, the method should wait and try again when appropriate. This means that the method should only return if the vehicle was successfully admitted in one of the tunnels and return that tunnel.
